    public class TimeLineImpl
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
implements TimeLine
    An implementation of the model object 'Time Line'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Bucket Type
    • Description
    • Time Zone ID
    • Locale Language
    • Locale Country
    • Horizon Start
    • Horizon End
    • Bucket
    • First Bucket
    • Last Bucket
